## Component rules

- **Buttons** â†’ Shadcn `<Button>` only. No raw `<button>` for interactive triggers.
- **Tables** â†’ Shadcn `<Table>` only. No raw `<table>`.
- **Cards** â†’ Shadcn `<Card>` family. No raw rounded divs masquerading as cards.
- **Inputs** â†’ Shadcn `<Input>` + `<Label>`. No raw `<input>`.
- **Tabs** â†’ Shadcn `<Tabs>` family.
- **Switches** â†’ Shadcn `<Switch>`.
- **Badges** â†’ Shadcn `<Badge>`.

## Dark mode

Light is `:root`. Dark is `.dark` class on `<html>`. Components must **never** branch on theme â€” read CSS variables and let the cascade do it.

```tsx
// âťŚ Don't
{isDark ? "#fff" : "#000"}

// âś… Do
style={{ color: "var(--color-text-primary)" }}
```

