# Agent delegation

This project ships specialized agents under `.claude/agents/`. **Use them.**

## When to delegate

| Task | Agent | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| **Add a page, component, token, or pattern** | **`design-agent`** | Encodes all design system rules. Use for almost any product-building task. |
| Pre-commit / pre-deploy full QA sweep | `qa-orchestrator` | Runs the next four agents in sequence + aggregates findings |
| Find hardcoded values in code | `code-scanner` | Read-only static analysis |
| Verify tokens stay in sync with docs + viewers | `token-auditor` | Read-only consistency check |
| Compare new screenshots vs committed baseline | `visual-diff` | Pixelmatch via `screenshots/` git HEAD |
| WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility audit | `a11y-checker` | axe-core via Playwright |

## How to invoke

```
/agents design-agent           # Build a feature
/agents qa-orchestrator        # Full QA sweep before merge
/agents code-scanner           # Just check for hardcoded values
```
